@startuml sequence-monitoring-penitipan
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center

title Sequence Diagram — Monitoring Harian Penitipan (Staff)

actor "Staff / Owner" as Staff
actor Pelanggan
participant "Aplikasi Web\n(Dashboard Internal)" as AppInt
participant "Aplikasi Web\n(Pelanggan)" as AppPel
participant "Backend API" as API
database "Database" as DB

Staff -> AppInt : Buka penitipan aktif
AppInt -> API : GET /internal/booking/penitipan?status=SEDANG_DITITIPKAN
API -> DB : SELECT booking_penitipan aktif
DB --> API : Daftar penitipan
API --> AppInt : Data penitipan
AppInt --> Staff : Tampilkan kucing sedang dititipkan

Staff -> AppInt : Pilih booking & input monitoring\n(foto, catatan makan, kondisi, aktivitas)
AppInt -> API : POST /internal/monitoring-penitipan
API -> API : Validasi booking status\n= SEDANG_DITITIPKAN
API -> DB : INSERT monitoring_penitipan\n(booking_id, staff_id, tanggal, ...)
DB --> API : monitoring_id
API -> DB : INSERT notifikasi\n(jenis=MONITORING_PENITIPAN,\npenerima=pelanggan_id)
DB --> API : OK
API --> AppInt : 201 Created
AppInt --> Staff : Monitoring tersimpan

API -> AppPel : Push / polling notifikasi baru
AppPel --> Pelanggan : Notifikasi update monitoring

Pelanggan -> AppPel : Buka detail penitipan
AppPel -> API : GET /booking/penitipan/{id}/monitoring
API -> DB : SELECT monitoring_penitipan\nORDER BY tanggal DESC
DB --> API : Riwayat monitoring
API --> AppPel : Data monitoring
AppPel --> Pelanggan : Tampilkan foto & catatan harian

@enduml
